.gradle/
build/
out/
run/
.idea/
*.iml

# Committed on purpose: these are the web builder's own export, and
# PresetContractTest parses them with the real codec. The blanket out/ rule
# above would otherwise drop them and break the build on a fresh clone.
!web/test/out/

# Committed on purpose: the builder page lives at web/build/ so its served URL
# is /build with no filename. The blanket build/ rule above would otherwise
# silently drop it from the repository.
!web/build/
